          The product is more about providing delightful experiences. When users
          browse a website or use an app, I strive to offer them the perfect
          balance between aesthetics and functionality—just like performing on
          stage, where every note must hit at the perfect moment. Similarly,
          every feature should appear exactly when the user needs it. As a
